caption.text: Frente a frente. Dos versiones con diferentes filosofías. Después de unos días con #switchlite he podido percibir cosas interesantes. La primera de todas, redescubrir el buen hacer de Nintendo con el primer modelo. Materiales más premium que el modelo Lite,  y una pantalla que se hace aún más grande, después de jugar a la Lite. De ahí, la diferencia de precio. Switch Lite, es más plástico, pero muy agradable al tacto, y sobretodo, ligero. Es lo más sorprendente, apenas notamos su peso. Su tamaño es el ideal para llevar en el bolsillo pequeño de la mochila, algo que suelo hacer con mis 3DS. La cruceta le sienta genial y jugar a juegos 2D es una delicia. Para los juegos de lucha, no es precisión absoluta, pero se puede jugar bastante bien. Destacaría sobretodo, su comodidad para jugar, más ergonomica que el modelo original, por su tamaño y peso. Creo que es la evolución lógica de 3DS, una portátil potente con una gran pantalla, que me trae recuerdos de otra gran portátil; la mítica PSP. Quizás Switch Lite, es el resultado de la evolución de las portátiles, la representante de un legado, que ha cobrado forma en un dispositivo que se acerca mucho a la consola portátil perfecta. PS Vita estuvo cerca de esa perfección. Recomendaría Switch Lite a todos aquellos que siguen usando su 3DS, y quieran seguir usando consolas portátiles. Fue diseñada para ocupar un sitio en tus pertenencias diarias. preview_comments.text: All'inizio ero scettico per questo gioco, ma mi sa che mi ricrederò
Hanno costruito un rapporto tra Thor e Cap pure qui😍

caption.text:
In un Q&A con i fan, il doppiatore Travis Willingham ha parlato  del Mjolnir abbandonato che compare nel primo trailer del gioco alla base del monumento dedicato a Captain America, spiegando:

Domanda: Vediamo un’immagine del martello di Thor abbandonato. La storia di Thor indegno è stata già esplorata in passato. Cosa rende questa versione unica e differente?

Risposta: Cap è l’unico umano che Thor reputa degno di sollevare Mjolnir, ed ha fallito. Non solo, i “mortali” stanno discutendo tra di loro e non riescono a tornare uniti senza il loro Capitano. Anche Thor non riesce ad assumere il suo ruolo. Farà quindi una scelta molto interessante che avrà conseguenze indesiderate che riecheggeranno per tutta la campagna e si svilupperanno completamente nella storia del gioco.

Il Dio del Tuono ha abbandonato l’arma dopo aver fallito e presumibilmente non si sente più degno di brandirla, scelta che potrebbe portare a una storia che vada a esplorare il significato del fallimento per l’eroe, oppure una sorta di adattamento dell’acclamata run The Unworthy Thor(Indegno Thor). Cosa ne pensate? . .
.
( Follow me for more ➡️ @marvel_dc_fanpage01 ) • Like ❤️ - Comment 💬 - Share 📤 • .
.
.

preview_comments.text: Dopo aver giocato tutti gli Uncharted questa è una delle notizie migliori che avrebbero potuto darmi. Sono sicura che Tom Holland riuscirà a fare giustizia giovane Drake. 😍❤️

caption.text:
Travis Knight sarà il regista del film su Uncharted con Tom Holland. C'è poco da fare: Knight è uno che sa quel che fa, visivamente soprattutto. Non so che si inventerà con la vegetazione e rocce. Comunque sarà il primo film di PlayStation Production e madonna se sono hypato per questo progetto di Sony. Mi fido di quell'uomo e Tom Holland ci sta come giovane Nathan Drake. Il film probabilmente uscirà a fine 2020 ~Lore

caption.text:
Here’s my #StackItUp for September! 
The two Club Penguin DS games were a couple of games I loved playing when I was younger.  I’m glad I was able to buy them back and for a good price 😉 (both CIB for $7 total)
GameStop prices their preowned games the same, regardless of what case they come in.  So, when I saw Shadow of the Tomb Raider in the steel book for a good price, I couldn’t pass it up ☺️ It’s a game I want to play, but will probably stay in the bottom of the backlog. 
I wasn’t sure if I was going to buy Borderlands 3 or not because I’m not big on FPS.  However, when I watched some streams of it, I caved and bought it!  I’m currently level 10 in the game so I’m not super far into it. 
Link’s Awakening I knew was a must-buy from the moment it was announced.  BoTW was the first Zelda game I really played and I’m anxious play through all of them 💚 I already finished the game and I 100%’d it EXCLUDING the Dampé stuff
The SNES game bundle of Dr Mario & Tetris was something I randomly stumbled upon in GameStop.  I was surprised to see a boxed SNES game and picked it up since it was in wonderful condition.  The box is a tiny bit beat up, but everything inside is in mint condition.
And that’s what I got this month!  There are a lot of games releasing in October that I want, but I’m going to try and only buy a few of them 🙈

Indonesian Culture Dress Up is a game dress Indonesian traditional clothing that can be played on Android. Indonesian Culture Dress Up features the Augmented Reality technology in the form of an image (marker), you must target an image (marker) in front of camera, after it emerged the image of custom clothing area, you must memorize the picture then press the Ready to Play to pair the clothes to the character to pair the dress code must conform to the image that appears on the image (the card). Keep enjoy and Discover Indonesian Culture .

Hey guys, we want to inform you that the early playtest phase is coming to an end in one week. Until this sunday (October 6th, 1pm UTC) you still have the chance to play the game (for Windows PC). If you haven’t done it already then join our discord server to generate your personal access key.

Indonesian Culture Dress Up is a game dress Indonesian traditional clothing that can be played on Android. Indonesian Culture Dress Up features the Augmented Reality technology in the form of an image (marker), you must target an image (marker) in front of camera, after it emerged the image of custom clothing area, you must memorize the picture then press the Ready to Play to pair the clothes to the character to pair the dress code must conform to the image that appears on the image (the card). Keep enjoy and Discover Indonesian Culture .
.

Silver Surfer is a video game released for the Nintendo Entertainment System, developed by Software Creations and released by Arcadia Systems in November 1990 in the United States. Silver Surfer is primarily known for its strong difficulty and highly praised music.
.
Silver Surfer received mostly mixed reviews. The music of the game, however, is highly praised for its composition and technical accomplishments.
.

I was in the Metal slug mood yesterday so I've draw one of my favourite characters from the game, Tarma. Metal Slug is a serie of video games produced by SNK for the Neo-Geo (arcade and console) , It was well known for its outstanding graphics for the time, a wonderful spriting job made by the devs. I absolutely love everything about this game, the artstyle, the ost, the wacky designes, and characters. But my favourite one is probably the 3rd entery in the series, not only because it was fun to play, but the game had a some funny jokes from time to time. It's the first time I try to draw in this type of artstyle, it has much more detail to it, and for a first time, it's not that bad, I think. I hope you'll like this new drawing. See ya. #SNK #metalslug #tarma #videogames #arcade #neogeo #fanart
